Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
I came all the way here to import things, but
there's nothing to buy. I'm so disappointed...

<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
I found a nice product, but there's only one left.
I can't make a profit with just one.

<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
I stocked up on all kinds of goods here. Cha-
ching!

<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
I've been traveling all over the world with my dad
since I was little... Man, this town has the best
goods anywhere!

<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
I came here looking for new products to import.

<NAME_MOB_ANDRE>
Veronica is so beautiful... If I only had the
guts...
